@9991  = ~Monstrous Evolution~
@9992  = ~Monstrous Evolution: this ability causes the psion's body to rapidly grow into a hideously powerful, hulking form. The monstrous form has an AC of -5, a THAC0 of 2 and attacks twice per round with powerful fists. These attacks do 3d6 crushing damage plus 2d4 poison damage. In this form the psion is immune to entanglement, web and hold effects, and to all poisons.

Upon resuming <PRO_HISHER> natural form, the psion becomes fatigued and suffers a 20-point temporary reduction in <PRO_HISHER> max hit points.~
